        "timestamp": "2019-10-09 13:24:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+2\n\nAs part of the Frankfurt SOL003 Adapter enhancement requirements, SOL003 Adapter NBI enhancement requirement and JIRA tickets have already been created. So, we can generalize the Create/Instantiate and Terminate/Delete NBI and the error handling based on the SOL003 spec. This will benefit for other ONAP SOL003 Adapter client (such as GNFC) to access the SOL003 Adapter in a standard way. So, we will leave this ticket as is (merged) and will discuss enhancement further.",
